{"tid":1901122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢疫區亂象】【大量外省捐助食物遭銷毀】","createTime":"2020-02-27T15:33:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T15:47:35.000Z","uid":39206,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"647a2baaa5d9af5a23f9a7d84ee3926366baff80","tid":1901122,"uid":39206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T15:33:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/RFA_Chinese/status/1233005601015259137?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRFA_Chinese%2Fstatus%2F1233005601015259137%3Fs%3D09&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0Z1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=82470b82\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRFA_Chinese%2Fstatus%2F1233005601015259137%3Fs%3D09&h=1dd777d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/RFA_Chinese/status/1233005601015259137?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n武漢疫區亂象】<br />\n【大量外省捐助食物遭銷毀】<br />\n【糧價卻居高不下】<br />\n近日網上不斷傳出武漢地區銷毀新鮮食物的視頻。本台記者詢問過當地志願組織工作人員，才發現原來當局為保證國營和大企業提供的糧食能保持在較高價格，以彌補高昂的運輸成本，故不惜銷毀從外省捐助過來的食物，這樣造成了極大的浪費。"},{"pid":"d58e16350e393f311fd19bf71ec8af168c5a6661","tid":1901122,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T15:34:51.000Z","msg":"【第貳拾柒期牆紙】 工會抗暴政<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1897739/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1897739/page/1</a><br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0Z1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=7e65b68d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\nFB : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F852wallpaper%2F&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0Z1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=ba17b5f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/</a><br />\nIG : <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hongkong_wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com